{
  "stem": "10829.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was already a bigger village, one of those villages.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, this was near Kiev.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was near Kiev, around there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went into deep Poland already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where was it-- not Katowice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I forgot the-- I think it was just outside Katowice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was going towards Kiev.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were-- then from there-- after we were free, part of this-- and this is a history all by itself.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- during the-- during the-- during the-- the-- the time where we were liberated, life in Europe, especially in Poland, the Russians hated the Ukraines.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Russians had as much animosity towards the Germans and the Ukraines as they-- and towards the Poles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a point where they-- where a Jew was already looked up a lot better than the-- right after the war than the Ukraine because the Ukraine and the Russians were very-- they were fighting against each other there.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when we were freed, the Russians used to use us to try to track down some of the Ukraines and the Pollacks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had a-- we had a pretty good life for a little bit down there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we used to catch a lot of the-- that we knew the Ukraines, so we used to catch them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they'd hang them right there on the bazaar and the market.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you'd have truckloads.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If we would go to some of our forest, our hiding out-- hideouts, and we'd find some of the-- of them, they used to bring them out and hang them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if you recognized them, that's all you had to do is say, yeah.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I remember them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they'd hang them right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And some of those women used to take the whips out of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
